This code always allow you to get in the boxes Power Items in any position that you are in the game. 
The item that you will get are: Bullet Bill, Golden Mushroom, Triple Mushroom, Star and all items
that the player always obtained when are in the last place. this code also affects other players 
in the online game, the code forces the server for other players to get the same items that you get. 
this only affects some players, especially when a race is among 10 or fewer players.

Replace X's with desired controller address and replace Y's with desired button activator.
See https://github.com/Megabyte918/MK8-Memory-Notes/blob/master/ACTIVATORS.md for more info.

